name: Space Lint
description: Inventory management game set in space. Loot items, craft and repair to survive!

name: Ghosts 4 Everybody
description: Fight countless armies of enemies with up to 4 players! Collect ghosts and gold from fallen enemies to become stronger. Dead players can still support the living players. The fight only ends when all players are dead!

name: Super Thrustforce: Orbital Meat Police
description: Super Thrustforce: Orbital Meat Police is an old-school arcade game featuring gravity-based gameplay and lots of shooting.

name: Deodato's Cannibal
description: Borneo: A Jungle Nightmare is an interactive horror graphic adventure, with the direction and script of Ruggero Deodato.Take control of different characters in a desperate expedition to the virgin jungles of Borneo.

name: Launched!
description: Launched! is a small scale RTS about building and launching an arsenal of missiles at the other island in the distance.

name: Mall Master
description: Mall Master - now you can design, build and manage shopping mall. Create your own successful business and make your customers happy. Mall Master gives you the opportunity to create a happy, stress-free work environment... of course, if you can do it.

name: Echo's Esker
description: You are lost in the catacombs and finding your way out won’t be easy, but upon reaching the surface you will find you are not the only one who is lost. The mysterious spirit hound Echo is far from home, but with her by your side, exploration is as simple as a game of fetch.

name: Spiritual Calling VR
description: A well-known detective-psychic receives a diary of a girl who studied at a boarding school for adopted children. She died in strange circumstances. In search of truth, you have to explore the school to demystify what happed there.

name: New King
description: New King is a strategy game with the theme of medieval management and adventure. Players will play as a newly enthroned king to protect his land and people from the invasion of the orcs.

name: Wasted World
description: Take over a disfunctional Waste Management Facility on a distant planet. Build incinerators, recyclers, robots, turrets, and more. Battle vicious creatures on the planet's surface with powerful weapons!

name: Wire
description: Wire is in charge of maintaining a telecommunications center. Ready to take his well-deserved holidays, the entire network goes offline. Help Wire restart the repeater present in each sector. Be careful tough! These sectors are a bit strange. Good luck!

name: Discreet
description: Are you a thief? Then your mission will be to steal the most objects without the owner seeing you. You are the owner ? You will do everything to protect your house, go for a stop thieves!

name: Unknown Ways
description: Buckle up and take a ride on this wholesome adventure to places you couldn't even imagine. Help this golem boy to find a way out of these forests and mountains.

name: Western Sigil
description: Western Sigil is a tower defense & resource management game with a dose of strategy, where you control units of unlikely allies. Shoot your way through the hordes of creatures and save Weird West from the spreading plague!

name: Party Arena
description: 2-4 Players Online or Local Play. Turn Based Strategy Board Game + Action Mini Games. Use items to max effect as you move around the board and combo to victory. Fast games (20 minutes total)! Fun for any evening or night with friends!

name: Movie World
description: In Movie World you can build your own movie studio. Produce entertaining and glamorous movies. Research new technologies to keep up with the industry. Expand into series, compete with other studios, receive the awards, create franchises and prevail in the movie business.

name: The Prodigal Soul
description: The Prodigal Soul - a "survival horror" with elements of a "shooter", where you have to find out what happened to the main character and find out the cause of a mental disorder, thereby unraveling the cause of the tragedy ...

name: Nine Chronicles
description: Utilising groundbreaking technology, Nine Chronicles is a fantasy MMORPG powered by the players, set in a world that can never be shut down. Infinitely moddable and owned by the community, Nine Chronicles invites you to aid the goddess Freya in her eternal struggle against an evil ravaging the land.

name: Minnade Counter Fight
description: "Minnade Counter Fight" is a ramen cooking game based on the VR Ramen Shop Simulator "Counter Fight" that allows up to four players to enjoy local multiplayer. Familiar customers and robbers also appear. Find a playable character full of personality that suits you and head to the kitchen right now.

name: I saw the night
description: FPP single-player adventure game with scarce but surprising and violent shooter scenes. Unsettling and insightful thriller spiked heavily with philosofical but witty rejoinders and wry humor. Made in Unreal Engine 4.

name: One of
description: It's a story about two souls who want to be understood, but finally hurt each other.

name: While (You) World.Create()
description: Solve puzzles by building different things for your automata! In the end, you will find that it is not just a video game...

name: Zatorski, Ph.D.
description: Indie-game in the genre of psychological adventure with the elements of rogue-like and visual novel. A meditative, thought-provoking simulator of an infinitely lonely old professor who's life and existence are questionable. Confusion, terror and despair are a part of a routine here.

name: Taimumari 2
description: 2D platformer, inspired by the best video games of the last century for people who are tired of metroidvanias. Someone has given the academy's students mysterious and dangerous powers, and Himari is about to find the truth.

name: Mossen Seikkailut
description: Mossen Seikkailut is an indie RPG adventure where you solve puzzles as a dog and face real-time fights on your way to glory. Gain respect by helping others and learn new fighting techniques to defeat those who oppose you. Experience all of this in magnificent 640x480 resolution!

name: Squirrel Forest
description: Deforestation is an apocalypse for squirrels. Only a few trees are left standing. Squirrels are put in danger and forced to act. Two brothers Zen and Ven decide to restore harmony in the forest by uniting fellow survivors and embarking on a journey to replant the forest. They need you to help them!

name: March of Soldiers
description: March Of Soldiers is a real time strategy single player , It is a military game based on the player's skill and the strength of his financial economy

name: Briefcase Inc.
description: A hardcore precision platformer where you switch between three differently skilled characters to collect briefcases and make your way through levels.

name: Dawn at my Neighbourhood
description: Dawn at my Neighborhood is a tribute to classic 90s games, reworked with new mechanics and graphics inspired by N64 and PlayStation.

name: MagiKart: Retro Kart Racing
description: MagiKart: Retro Kart Racing is a retro inspired racing game that heavily borrows from some of the best (and worst) late 90s kart racers.

name: Space Station Manager
description: Space Station Manager is an exciting game where you own a space company, your main goal is to build a space station, make profit, grow your business, build an economical network, and expand beyond the solar system.

name: Cloudscape
description:
Cloudscape is an open-world action adventure survival game.

You play as Kumo, a Cloudling who awakes on an uninhabited island. Explore the island and gather resources to make tools to help you survive and adventure further. At night, strange monsters will appear, ready to attack. Prepare yourself and keep a fire going to make it through the night. Survive long enough to escape the island and uncover new islands with new places to explore, new faces, and much more.

name: Digitizer
description: Digitizer is a Sci-Fi action RPG set in a post-capitalist world. It’s a story-driven open-world game with multiple factions. Fight, craft, drive and make your story choices that will bring the conflict to its end.

name: Cubic Chess
description: Cubic Chess is a twist on traditional Chess, setting the pieces onto a 3d cubic board, you can rotate, revolve and plan around the board itself and is perfect for players that want a new way to think of their favorite game, without too many more bells and whistles.

name: Holmgang: Memories of the Forgotten
description: Dracorum was a land of peace and prosperity, but King Haziel's death caused darkness and wickedness over the kingdom. Everything seems lost, but three heroes will rise against injustice... It is time to know their stories.

name: SCP: Recontainment
description: Experience singleplayer and multiplayer initial containments, decontaminations and encounters with many of the SCP Foundation's scariest and most mysterious SCPs in the most ambitious SCP game to date.

name: Axeson's Fury VR
description: Axeson's Fury VR throws you into an intensely combative arcade style virtual reality environment that will have you fighting for your life and that of your family as society is turned by dark unknown forces. Become John Axeson and be all you can be... one mean slick fighting machine!

name: Chicaro Dentistry
description: It's a dental simulation game that treats a cow who visits a space shuttle dentist. It's a game where you can use the tools you need to cure tooth decay to heal a child's cavity.

name: Farm Your Friends
description: A fast-paced couch competitive farming game for up to 8 players. This farming life isn't as calm and peaceful as you'd expect: to become the best farmer you will need unusual methods to prevent your enemies from succeding.

name: Panzer Crew VR
description: A multiplayer tank deathmatch game where each tank is manned by three players: the commander, the driver and the gunner. Up to four tanks can battle for a total of 12 players. Can your crew work as a unit or will you devolve into chaos and be annihilated?

name: Hexagon Heroes
description: Hexagon Heroes is a turn-based strategy game about controlling the map while balancing economics, military tactics and technology to overwhelm and destroy other players.

name: Realm Hacker
description: Realm Hacker is a game based on cyber worlds and hackers, allowing you to manipulate characters while building blocks, while using dexterous movement to pass the game level.

name: Grids of World
description: Grids of World is an indie game developed by individual based on Tic-Tac-Toe principle.There are 9 strongholds in game,winning rules require players to occupy three consecutive strongholds forming a line.You can play with computer or online players to experience Team strategy and individual battle.

name: Crystal Soul Chambers
description: Crystal Soul chambers is a roguelike card game where you must create a group of 3 characters, each one with his own unique card set. Each of the characters has their own abilities related to their personality!

name: Hand Cannon Virtuoso
description: Hand Cannon Virtuoso is a VR Roguelite Bullet Hell where you Build your Arsenal by Collecting Cards. Fight your way to the top of a shape-shifting tower filled with powerful foes!

name: Taravana
description: In Taravana you will discover a post-apocalyptic underwater world filled with danger and mystery. Сraft items and equipment to improve your diving gear, explore the dismal ocean depths, survive the deadly hazards and savage enemies - or perish trying...

name: Project Toon Tanks
description: Welcome to Project Toon Tanks! Epic battle arenas where two players (or one player and an AI if you are ... taking a break) fight to the death. Nothing is historically accurate here and that is AWESOME!

name: Smashing Healthy VR
description: Smashing Healthy VR is a fitness game for those people who are willing to be healthy. Smash the box if you want to be healthy!

name: Oh Frog
description: Oh Frog is a loopy 2D action adventure game set in the mysterious, fairy tale-esque lands of the Frog Kingdom. Play as Lif, the Frog Kingdom’s bravest frog, as you travel through gorgeous, lovingly hand-drawn landscapes and animated worlds, on your quest to recover the stolen Crowns of Power!

name: Super fight
description: A arcade style action game, come to start your fight

name: NoWaitHero
description: Deck building card battle "NoWaitHero" There is no need to wait during a duel. Seize the victory ahead of the choice.

name: Waves of Death VR
description: Following the tragic mistake of military scientists, a new generation of a viral compound has spread through the city allowing the dead to come back to life... All the dead, but also the bloodthirsty Bosses. Jake has to cross the city to save his loved-ones.The countdown begins!

name: Survival Denied
description: Survival Denied is a casual zombie shooter, made primarily with VR in mind. Wide choice of weapons, perks and power-ups make the game interesting. Dive in and try to survive as long as you can!

name: My Company and I Fell Into an RPG
PsyHotel
description: Take on the role of the owner of a cosy hotel off the beaten path of civilization. Just remember that all your clients are criminals and psychopaths. Take care of them properly, starting with thieves and ending with fat fishes. You are the law here!

name: Soulborn
description:
If you mix Zelda and The Witcher you will get SOULBORN; a story driven open world RPG-ADVENTURE based on exploration, combat and character development. The world is inspired by the NORSE MYTHOLOGY and the conflict of humans living in the absence of the fallen gods. 
 
Play on the side of Thor’s mighty hammer MJOLNIR which came to life and TRANSFORMS into different weapons and creatures to support your journey. Level up your character, fight against a lot of different enemies, solve DUNGEONS & PUZZLES and master your abilities to defeat the ultimate beast Nidhöggr and stop the RAGNARÖK. 
 
Explore a vast OPEN WORLD, secret places and interact with a fully immersive breathtaking environment. Discover UNIQUE BIOMES and their thrilling inhabits.

name: Mini Motor Racing X: Digital Deluxe Edition
Cinderstone Online
description: Cinderstone Online is a cute and colorful MMORPG. Protect the world from the rivalry gods wanting their stolen lands back. Climb your way for glory, farming, trading, conquering and becoming the ruler of a region. Explore and find new locations filled with rewarding loot and mysteries to uncover.

name: Iced In
description:
Help! Penguins have gotten themselves into quite the pickle! Can you solve all 50 puzzles and free each one? 
 
 
Simply push blocks of ice around until they all come to rest on a switch to rescue each penguin from their cage! Don't let the adorable penguins fool you.. Iced In gets tough!

name: Elemental Strike: Mirage Tower
description:
There are five main elements in the world: wind, fire, water, earth and lightning. With these elements, build towers and fight against the enemy hordes that threaten our lands. Each element has both strengths and weaknesses. Power-up and combine up to three elements to forge new towers each with their own abilities. 
 
Some towers have skills that you can target and activate while others provide passive bonuses. Craft your own tower build and placement strategies to optimize their support of each other to win

name: Beberserker
description:
Inspired by 90s FPS and frenetic arcade games, Beberserker is a fast-paced FPP (First person Puncher) in which you must defeat Satan’s Offspring using your bare hands. Taking advantage of the movement versatility your hits provide, you must defeat as many babies as you can. 
 
•	Play in browser. You don’t need to download the game! 
•	Use our leaderboard system to compete against your friends. 
•	Prove your might and enter our “Infernal Altar”. 
•	Brutal progressive metal soundtrack.

name: Divinoids
description: Divinoids is a desperate struggle between a society much like our own, and highly advanced aliens piloting shapeshifting mechanical monstrosities... where you play as the aliens.

name: Crash Test Launcher
description: in this game players control a range of cars and bikes to crash test. once they have crashed it, they need to go as far as possible to get as much money which they can then use for gaining more cars and upgrades.

name: Killer Freaks From Outer Space
description:
Killer Freaks from Outer Space is a cancelled game project from Ubisoft Montpellier that was changed to better fit the Wii U platform after being shown at E3 201.
It was re-revealed as ZombiU at E3 2012.

"In 2012, the world is going down the drain, fast...

Reams of alien ships have crashed into our planet, and these big wads of diseased, planet-eating, phlegm are spawning hordes of insanely vicious killers! The dangerous and degenerate creatures from outer space we call FREAKS seek to eradicate the human species with single-minded fury.

You're a survivor; a winner -- humanity's only freaking hope! Those raunchy aliens missed their chance to put you and your buddies down. And now you're going to make them regret it -- one slimy alien body-part at a time!

Immerse yourself in this psychotic, arcade-style, 4-player co-op shooter; and just try and keep your head..."

name: Techno Cop
description:
A fast-paced first-person shooter in a parkour obstacle course style level. 
The game has a 7 second time limit at the start of a level which increases when enemies are killed. 
The game was designed to be a small project and had been made around the idea of setting high scores and competing over them with friends. 
 
It was teased at some pax events in 2017 by 3D Realms and Slipgate Ironworks, Slipgate Studios at the time, before the project was canceled to work on a similar but larger scale game in Ghostrunner with the company One More Level.

name: Motherflakker
description:
A canceled game prototype from 3D Realms/Slipgate Ironworks, made during the development of Ion Fury, based on the idea of an Ion Fury/Bombshell game in a late 1990s to early 2000s first-person shooter style. 
 
The project, for PC and Switch, was playable and had an internal demo using an arena shooter survival mode against increasingly difficult enemies.

name: Fate (Carnivale Card Game)
description: The Carnivale Game, Based on the Hit HBO series, is a addictive card game based around tarot cards.

name: S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Dead Air
description: S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Dead Air a full-scale modification based on Call of Chernobyl. It changes all aspects of the game, from graphics, audio, and special effects to various gameplay and AI features. The modification evolves from the ideas started in Call of Misery, a previous project from the mod’s author. Major inspirations for Dead Air have been projects such as NLC, MISERY, Autumn Aurora, and OGSE. Dead Air prioritizes the development of the game platform’s potential, gameplay complexity, and attention to detail, along with addressing both the quality and quantity of all content.

name: Rift Frigate
description: Rift Frigate is a dynamic space shooter that combines vehicular combat with a good old FPS arsenal, unfolding a gripping story with surreal cosmic visuals.

name: Panzer Campaigns: Japan '46
description:
With the successful completion of Operation Olympic, the Allies had establish air bases and naval ports on the southern half of the Japanese home island of Kyushu from which they could be used for Operation Coronet. Panzer Campaigns: Japan '46 - Operation Coronet covers the invasion of the Japanese home island of Honshu with the goal being to capture Tokyo and the factories and farmland of the
Kanto Plain. Coronet would have been the largest invasion of the war. Two Allied armies, composed of eleven corps, would have participated in the campaign.

name: Thing Thing Collection
description:
The Complete Collection of Thing Thing Games, as well as a few extras on the side, packed neatly in this little launcher courtesy of GameDevDan (https://forum.yoyogames.com/index.php?threads/game-launcher-create-your-own-game-packs.47236)

This includes:
Thing Thing
Thing Thing 2
Thing Thing 3
Thing Thing 4
Thing Thing Arena
Thing Thing Arena 2
Thing Thing Arena 3
Thing Thing Arena Pro
Thing Thing Arena Classic
Thing Thing 2: Alpha
Thing Thing Maker
The Thing Thing 4 Trailer
And a Guide.

The Guide is a compilation of the official ones on Crazymonkeygames.com with the Author Commentary from Newgrounds.com

You DO NOT NEED Adobe Flash to run any of these games, they come converted to .exe for your convenience.

I Also included a few images so you can add this launcher to your Steam Library, with and without hyphen, it's up to you which one is correct.

If you have the original Thing Thing Alpha or an offline version of the Thing Thing ARENA CL@$$IC H@X!! please let me know so I can add them to the collection.

All Thing Thing Content belongs to Diseased Productions Games.
Please support the official releases at /

name: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Keppuu Kengeki Royale
description: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Keppuu Kengeki Royale (Kimetsu no Yaiba: Blood-Stench Blade Royale) is an asymmetric battle arena action game based on the manga and television adaptation Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba. Players will be able to join both the Demon Slayers Corps or the Demon team in this game. The two sides need to fight each other in a match. If players choose to be on the Demon Slayers Corps, they will be able to use different breathing techniques and their goal is to slay the demons. If players choose to be on the Demon team, they will be able to use various demon powers and their goal is to kill all demon slayers. With completely different destinies, let's join the battle of life in the game!

name: Sin: Reloaded
description: Nightdive Studios and 3D Realms have joined forces to bring you SiN: Reloaded, a completely remastered experience of the classic 1998 shooter from Ritual Entertainment. SiN was a groundbreaking story driven FPS brimming with memorable characters, horrific enemies and a devastating arsenal that pushed the Quake II Engine to its limits. Now in 2020 SiN has been Reloaded!

name: Donkey Kong: Coconut Crackers
description:
Donkey Kong Coconut Crackers is a canceled puzzle game for the Game Boy Advance and a Donkey Kong spinoff title. The game was developed by Rare Ltd., and was originally planned for a November 2001 release date. It was likely postponed ahead of time due to the forthcoming acquisition from Microsoft in 2002. However, the game was eventually converted into It's Mr. Pants, released in late 2004.

Some of the planned modes included various challenges around Donkey Kong Island, challenges from Cranky Kong, and a multiplayer mode.

name: Return of Donkey Kong
description:
Return of Donkey Kong is a canceled Nintendo Entertainment System game whose existence is attested in Nintendo of America publications from 1987 and 1988. It was featured as an upcoming game in the Official Nintendo Player's Guide in 1987.

Not much is known about the title aside from the fact that it was considered a follow-up to Donkey Kong, Donkey Kong Jr., Donkey Kong Jr. Math and Donkey Kong 3. The two blurbs describing the game suggest that barrel-throwing would return as a mechanic, and that Donkey Kong would appear as a playable character for the first time. No images were ever shown of the game and it is not known if Return of Donkey Kong ever existed past the conceptual stage.

name: Donkey Kong no Ongaku Asobi
description: Donkey Kong no Ongaku Asobi is a canceled game set for release on the Family Computer. It would have followed Popeye no Eigo Asobi and released alongside Donkey Kong Jr. Math as one of the edutainment games based on the Famicom's launch titles. Donkey Kong no Ongaku Asobi starred the cast of Donkey Kong and Donkey Kong Jr. The game never surfaced, and seems to have only been announced in 1983 in a Japanese handbill as well as magazines.

name: Diddy Kong Racing Adventure
description: Diddy Kong Racing Adventure is a rejected pitch made by the Climax Group for a Diddy Kong Racing sequel on the Nintendo GameCube around 2004. The project was never announced to the public in any capacity and only became known after an amateur video game archivist acquired the prototype and published a video about it in November 2016. Only the demo for their pitch was developed, in around April 2004, running on Xbox hardware as the tools had already been developed at the time.

name: Tvori
description: With Tvori you can create story prototypes such as animatics & previs, prototype XR apps, and make complete animated films. Export your work as videos, 360 videos, photos, 360 photos, VR experiences, and 3D models with animations.

name: Virtual Escape - The Play Room
description:
Virtual Escape: The Play Room is a 3D virtual reality game designed for the HTC Vive with support for Oculus Rift. Here you interact with objects and find the layered clues to reach your ultimate goal. 
 
Gameplay takes you on an engaging journey through a family's emotional trauma, with twists and surprises along the road. 
 
The atmospheric feel and interaction develops a deep connection with the characters that begs to be explored deeper. Taking place within a single room, you must find the clues and complete the challenging puzzles on the way to fulfil your achievement awards. 
 
With realistic graphics and intuitive interaction, Virtual Escape: The Play Room is an experience you won’t want to miss.

name: Medal of Honor: Pacific Assault - Director's Edition
Jumping jet
description:
Jumping jet is a challenging arcade game about flying through platforms while trying to avoid setting a trap of or flying into them 
 
The game is all about fun puzzles to solve, improving your reaction skills 
 
At the moment the game is under development which means from the 10 areas of the game only 1 is fully finished and public

name: Natural Balance: Chronicles
description:
Natural Balance: Chronicles is an unprecedented isometric Action RPG where your actions, along with the actions of other players, affect the world itself and everyone in it through the unique energy system with its innovative gameplay mechanics and events!

With each release of its episodic design, choose between two natural enemies and experience their independent journeys as they struggle with the harmful acts caused by the opposing race, as each side fights to sustain sufficient levels of their respective energy in order to survive.

name: Glory of Portugal: Fortresses of Brazil
description:
Glory of Portugal: Fortresses of Brazil take place in the colonial Brazil. The Portuguese, Dutch, French, British, Spanish and the native tribes will fight to control this territory. 
It's a first and third person shooter, single-player game. The player control vehicles like portuguese galleons and pirate ships. 
In the game you can see fortresses from Brazilian cities like Recife, Natal, Bertioga and Florianópolis.

name: HackRack
description:
HackRack is a game where you live in a city and use your hacking skills to influence the world around you.
The player will encounter many people and organizations, and their hacks will impact the world around them. The player will need to expand their living space and secret server room to accommodate computing racks, which can be customized to provide the power, traits, and abilities that their viruses require to overcome even the most secure of systems.

name: Project G.G.
description: A new game and IP from PlatinumGames that was followed by the announcement of a new development focused studio/division, PlatinumGames Tokyo, that was established with the investment funds from Tencent.

name: True Survivor
description: True Survivor is a cool game, which takes place in a provincial city, lost somewhere in Russia. Bad guys are in the city, dreaming of destroying the main character. Agent Red acts as the main hero of the game, and a whole army of cyborgs and hordes of zombies confront him.

name: [Grand Prototype]
description: Drive races and build your own vehicle. Find your racetrack on one of many maps. Try it out if you feel like it and beat your best time. But the game is not yet finished, from time to time it will expand and offer even more options.

name: Cockhead: Big Kahuna Bar
description: Our days, godforsaken place, somewhere on the Mexican border. The sheriff, who had packed his belongings in a cardboard box a long time ago, was going to vacate the office and take a long-awaited rest, while this case was supposed to be the final, unremarkable chord of his career.

name: Spellbind Tactics
description: Spellbind Tactics is a turn-based online competitive multiplayer game, where you control a small team of unique characters. Synergies and strategies are key in order to achieve victory. The game is still early in development so stay tuned for news.

name: Kaiju Fishing
description: Fish for giant monsters in an epic adventure! Explore Tropical, Arctic, and Lava habitats. Collect your favorite monster fish. Craft the perfect bait. Puzzles and Quests await.

name: MOLC's Daily Life of S.P.R.I.T.E.S.
description: You've arrived at City of FUK with a couple of crumpled bills in your pocket and a whole heap of opportunities ahead of you. You can do anything and everything you've ever wanted to do with your life in this mysterious city. Explore the stories of S.P.R.I.T.E.S.

name: Nihon Pro Mahjong Kishikai Kanshuu: Pro ni naru Mahjong DS
Welcome To... Chicheser OVN 3 : The Mysterious Affair At The Violet Hotel
Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku o! Fantasutikku Deizu
Invisible
description:
Invisible, is a single-player game with the goal of sending chills down your spine.
Invisible is a first person horror game. Utilizing endless tension, exceptional 3D graphics, and a horrifying soundscape, this game is crafted to scare your pants off!

name: Where's Waldo? for the Windows Phone
Backgammon
description: Backgammon is one of the oldest known board games. Its history can be traced back nearly 5,000 years to archaeological discoveries in Persia and Mesopotamia. It is a two-player game where each player has fifteen pieces (checkers or men) that move between twenty-four triangles (points) according to the roll of two dice. The objective of the game is to be first to bear off, i.e. move all fifteen checkers off the board.

name: Star Trek
description: A Star Trek themed game for the R-Zone.

name: Squares
description: Squares is a relaxed multi player game with out any combat and can be played by anyone of any age... meant for 2 or more players

name: Mass Effect
description: The heavily anticipated continuation of the Mass Effect series.

name: Untitled Lord of the Rings MMO
description:
Amazon Games are developing and publishing a new massively multiplayer online (MMO) game based on The Lord of the Rings by J.R.R. Tolkien.

The deal is the first major partnership to come to light since Embracer Group bought the rights to the Tolkien properties with its acquisition of Middle-earth Enterprises. Middle-earth Enterprises is now part of Embracer’s Freemode division.

The upcoming game will be an open-world MMO adventure in a persistent world set in Middle-earth, featuring the beloved stories of The Hobbit and The Lord of the Rings literary trilogy.

name: Voyager
description: Confront alien adversaries, explore uncharted planets, and unravel the mysteries of the cosmos. Customize your spacecraft, engage in epic space battles, and decide the fate of humanity. Become the hero the galaxy craves – are you up for the challenge?

name: Madden Football
description: Long before EA's reign on the football circuit, CBS was working on a multiplatform title with John Madden.

name: The War of Genesis III Part.2
Mobile Minigames: Play & Earn
description: Create your own heroes & take them into battle!

name: The Lord of the Rings Online Trading Card Game
description: Based on the physical Lord of the Rings Trading Card Game, LOTROTCG was a digital version of that game played online.

name: Hide and Seek
description: Hide and Seek is a stealth action FPS game that is similar to popular asymmetric multi-player games in PC and mobile platforms, however, was reinterpreted into VR platform.

name: Karaoke Joysound Wii: DX Deluxe Edition
Star Trek: The Next Generation - Trivia
4Stroy: Origin
description: 4Story places players in the disputed Iverian continent during the three Kingdoms era after the three Kings have successfully divided a once united nation. Now, they must prepare themselves as the balance of power shifts toward the unknown as treachery lurks in.

name: Abyss
description: Abyss is an arcade-adventure game telling the story of a teenager who sets off on a dangerous and obstacle-filled journey. Take part in this thrilling adventure, explore 21 different levels, from the gloomy streets of Łódź to the infernal dungeons.

name: Reborn: Survival
description: Welcome to a new survival experience with RPG elements and PVE Content. It is up to you, how you will survive this apocalyptic world. Team up with other survivors or fight them. Loot, Gear up, fight!

name: NSYNC Hotline Phone and Fantasy CD-Rom Game
Star Trek: Judgment Rites Movie & Sound Pack
Fast Tracks: The Computer Slot Car Construction Kit
Snow Fall
description:
Craft elements:
Metal x3 = chip
Chip x3 = Charge
Crystal x3 = Shard

Craft weapon:
Metal + metal + chip = rifle
Metal + wood + gear = automatic rifle
Metal + gear + board = machine gun
Crystal + board + gear = laser rifle
Shard + board + pinion = laser machine gun

Cinema
description: Cinema is an immersive investigative thriller game where player wields control over time and the intricate interplay of cause and effect within the storyline inspired by silent films.

name: Virtuverse
description: Virtuverse is a Sci-Fi RCE MMORPG. Combining an intuitive economy system with action-based gameplay. Virtuverse has no class restrictions, use any weapon or armour. Those who wish to seek adventure will be able to explore Virtuverse on their own or with friends.

name: Game Book DS: Koukaku no Regios
The Adventures of Death: Episode One - Emo Harvest on the Oregon Trail
Gem Jam
description: Can you solve the Puzzle of the Gems? GEM JAM features challenging "match three" puzzle play with a twist: you choose where the groups of gems are placed. Oh, and did we mention that the chest is shrinking so you will need to hurry.

name: Golf Keeper
description: This is not the golf that is known to many. Here are your rules. Can you score the ball in the hole?

name: Elementals
description: Mental Elementals is a 1 – 4 player twin stick shooter game. Player must use their element to fight through the level and reach the end as quickly as possible. Player’s can combine elements to create interesting effects.

name: Lasting Solstice
description: After suffering from amnesia, Kazu tries his best to regain his former self. Without his memories, he has trouble remembering close friends and family. With the help of old and new friends along the way, Kazu slowly goes on to his path through self-discovery.

name: Dread
description: Dread is a 4 player online co-op survival horror game. Explore haunted environments ranging from abandoned manors, the underground catacombs below Paris, abandoned schools and more in realistic detail. Trust No One: Sometimes death isn't the end. Play together in VR or standard game-play.

name: Color Blocks - Relax Puzzle
description: New guessing game in the genre of puzzles for adults and children. If you want to meditate and relax alone with yourself, then you have found the best solution. Turn on your brain and color lines in vibrant and vibrant colors. Select points on the playing field and watch how the blocks are painted over.

name: DokeV
description: DokeV is a creature-collecting open world action-adventure filled with intriguing stories and set in a unique, vibrant world. Befriend the adorable Dokebi that gain strength from and encourage people's dreams, and get ready to embark on an adventure!

name: Shape Palette
description: Shape Palette is a 2D logic puzzle game, manipulate shapes in order to venture through levels that are sure to test out your skills!

name: Tir et But: Edition Champions du Monde
Shot One
description: Part sports game, part arcadey shmup, all intergalactic adventure! Follow Volley and Vlad through their quest to reach the top in Shot One!

name: Sentient: Arena Mech Royale
description: Sentient is a new combat sport which involves controlling powerful mechs via augmented reality and going head to head in a battle royale with other mechs, these battles are broadcast worldwide

name: Kuma no Pooh-San: 100 Acre no Mori no Cooking Book
Lawl
description: Lawl is a Massive Multiplayer Online RPG, created for the people who loves this game style. Even since Lawl is a modern and advanced game, it also have a unique and classic graphic. We are in beta, so many things can change, and you can be a part of it.

name: Kutsushita Nyanko: Kutsushita o Haita Neko to Kurashi Hajime Mashita

name: Death Carnival
description: Welcome to Death Carnival, the fast-paced top-down parkour shooter. Insane assortment of weapons & characters, and a controller-smashing experience that will leave you hungry for more. Play story campaign solo, co-op with friends, or destroy everyone in PvP. Cross-platform and packed with spectator and party modes so the fun never ends. Choose from over a dozen characters each with unique attacks and story campaigns.

name: Cosmotrons
description: Cosmotrons is a cosmic battleground where skill and strategy collide. Choose your ship and customize its weaponry, engage in epic dogfights, navigate treacherous environments and outmaneuver your opponents in intense, fast-paced multiplayer battles. Are you ready to become a true space ace?

name: Dramatic Past
description: Delve into our protagonist’s past as she challenges a robot dictatorship with the help of a mysteriously sentient toaster.
